name: Capital Group International Equity Select ETFTM (Canada)
longDescription: The Fund invests primarily in a broad range of equity or equity-type securities including depositary receipts. The Fund may invest in issuers in developed and developing countries; a significant portion of its assets may be invested in issuers in developing countries Fund seeks Longterm growth of capital.
